Text:
This is pretty good clear resolution, and complete film.  I particularly enjoyed the text file furnished with it. It was amusing, as well as informative. Thanks.
By the way, this is a traditionally historic picture, and memorable. Credit where credit is due, Clifton Webb really stole the show, and I'm glad they brought him into this main 'talkie' since his silent film days.
thanks a lot, one of the best noir films
